<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 20:07:33 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>阿米猜·奇克利 (Amichai Chikli) 辞去以色列社会平等部长职务，将继续担任侨民事务部长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/chikli-to-resign-as-israels-social-equality-minister-remains-diaspora-affairs-minister/0000018c-ea6d-d0e9-a3de-feed5e7a0000</link><description>这位部长通知以色列总理，他将辞去职务，因为内塔尼亚胡政府因在战争期间维持 31 个办公室而浪费资源而受到公众批评</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 19:53:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/chikli-to-resign-as-israels-social-equality-minister-remains-diaspora-affairs-minister/0000018c-ea6d-d0e9-a3de-feed5e7a0000</guid></item><item><title>“现实已经暂停”：来自以色列加沙前线和黎巴嫩边境的报道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-08/ty-article/.highlight/reality-has-been-suspended-reporting-from-israels-front-lines-in-gaza-and-the-north/0000018c-e998-d249-a1ce-efddef3e0000</link><description>国土报记者安谢尔·普费弗（Anshel Pfeffer）和巴尔·佩莱格（Bar Peleg）最近加入了驻加沙城和黎巴嫩边境的以色列国防军部队。他们的快讯讲述了来自各种可能背景的以色列人的故事，他们的生活在三个月前发生了巨大的变化</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 19:48:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-08/ty-article/.highlight/reality-has-been-suspended-reporting-from-israels-front-lines-in-gaza-and-the-north/0000018c-e998-d249-a1ce-efddef3e0000</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，以色列转向对叙利亚境内与伊朗有关的目标进行更致命的打击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/israel-shifts-to-deadlier-strikes-on-iran-linked-targets-in-syria-sources-say/0000018c-ea56-df6f-ad8e-ea776a280000</link><description>尽管以色列多年来一直在叙利亚袭击与伊朗有关的目标，但据多个消息来源称，以色列现在对叙利亚境内的伊朗武器转运和防空系统发动了更致命、更频繁的空袭</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 19:16:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/israel-shifts-to-deadlier-strikes-on-iran-linked-targets-in-syria-sources-say/0000018c-ea56-df6f-ad8e-ea776a280000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯地道、伏击和友军火力的恐惧：加沙城以色列国防军士兵的 24 小时生活</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hamas-tunnels-ambushes-and-fear-of-friendly-fire-24-hours-with-idf-soldiers-in-gaza-city/0000018c-e8cd-d765-ab9d-f8fdd47b0000</link><description>在Shujaiyeh的大部分时间都是在等待中度过，每次回家都是经过精心计划的，敌人从地洞里钻出来的危险时刻存在。这些以色列国防军预备役军人现役已进入第四个月，距离纳哈尔奥兹只有五分钟路程</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 17:44:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hamas-tunnels-ambushes-and-fear-of-friendly-fire-24-hours-with-idf-soldiers-in-gaza-city/0000018c-e8cd-d765-ab9d-f8fdd47b0000</guid></item><item><title>八家外国航空公司将于下个月恢复飞往以色列的部分航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/eight-foreign-airlines-to-resume-partial-service-to-israel-over-the-next-month/0000018c-e9f7-d0e9-a3de-ffff05800000</link><description>如果安全局势恶化，包括法航、波兰LOT和西班牙Vueling在内的八家公司预计将撤回重新启动服务的决定</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 17:20:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/eight-foreign-airlines-to-resume-partial-service-to-israel-over-the-next-month/0000018c-e9f7-d0e9-a3de-ffff05800000</guid></item><item><title>科学发现猪节食的秘密</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-01-08/ty-article-magazine/science-discovers-secret-of-dieting-in-pigs/0000018c-e9d8-d249-a1ce-efdd11220000</link><description>研究表明，胶囊内的微型电机可以欺骗胃，让其误以为它已经吃饱了，从而导致猪吃得更少，虽然很小，但很有趣</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 16:57:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-01-08/ty-article-magazine/science-discovers-secret-of-dieting-in-pigs/0000018c-e9d8-d249-a1ce-efdd11220000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦伊斯兰圣战组织发布了以色列在加沙被扣为人质的视频</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-islamic-jihad-publishes-video-of-israeli-held-hostage-in-gaza/0000018c-e9c3-d249-a1ce-efc727f50000</link><description>10 月 7 日，47 岁的埃拉德·卡齐尔 (Elad Katzir) 和他的母亲汉娜 (Hanna) 在尼尔奥兹基布兹 (Kibbutz Nir ​​Oz) 的家中被绑架，随后汉娜作为人质交易的一部分被释放。他的父亲拉米在袭击中被杀</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 16:32:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-islamic-jihad-publishes-video-of-israeli-held-hostage-in-gaza/0000018c-e9c3-d249-a1ce-efc727f50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列部长建议重新安置加沙平民以“改善他们的生活状况”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-suggests-relocating-gazans-in-order-to-improve-their-living-situation/0000018c-e98e-d249-a1ce-efcfafb80000</link><description>奥兹玛·耶胡迪特部长阿米凯·埃利亚胡是最新一位表示支持加沙人“自愿移民”出自己家园的以色列联盟议员。这些评论可能会在海牙国际法院即将进行的审判中用于针对以色列</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 15:42:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-suggests-relocating-gazans-in-order-to-improve-their-living-situation/0000018c-e98e-d249-a1ce-efcfafb80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与真主党的战争对双方来说都是毁灭性的，那么为什么它感觉不可避免呢？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/an-israel-hezbollah-war-would-be-devastating-for-both-so-why-does-it-feel-inevitable/0000018c-e982-d249-a1ce-efc7a3b70000</link><description>也许以色列与真主党在黎巴嫩的军事对抗最不祥的事情是，人们感觉这是已成定局。也许不是加沙战争的延伸，但在不久的将来的某个时候</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 15:32:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/an-israel-hezbollah-war-would-be-devastating-for-both-so-why-does-it-feel-inevitable/0000018c-e982-d249-a1ce-efc7a3b70000</guid></item><item><title>真主党证实高级指挥官在以色列对黎巴嫩南部的袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-confirms-senior-commander-killed-in-israeli-attributed-strike-in-south-lebanon/0000018c-e972-d249-a1ce-ef77f0cf0000</link><description>真主党拉德万部队高级军官维萨姆·塔维尔被暗杀的罪魁祸首是以色列。据安全官员称，塔维尔在该组织的行动中发挥了重要作用。内塔尼亚胡总理表示，他将尽一切努力“恢复北部的安全”</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 15:21:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-confirms-senior-commander-killed-in-israeli-attributed-strike-in-south-lebanon/0000018c-e972-d249-a1ce-ef77f0cf0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议员签署请愿书指责以色列在加沙实施种族灭绝，引起议会轩然大波</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-mk-causes-uproar-in-knesset-after-signing-petition-accusing-israel-of-genocide/0000018c-e918-db55-a39e-ff9c0cf70000</link><description>在阿拉伯犹太人哈达什-塔阿尔党的议员奥弗·卡西夫签署南非请愿书后，议会其他成员呼吁将他罢免。卡西夫解释了他的理由，称“我的宪法义务是对以色列社会负责”，而不是对呼吁“种族清洗甚至实际种族灭绝”的政府负责</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 14:35:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-mk-causes-uproar-in-knesset-after-signing-petition-accusing-israel-of-genocide/0000018c-e918-db55-a39e-ff9c0cf70000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯来到中东清理以色列给美国造成的混乱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/blinken-comes-to-middle-east-to-clean-up-the-mess-israel-has-made-for-the-u-s/0000018c-e7b7-db55-a39e-f7b7ec0d0000</link><description>这是战争爆发以来第四次中东之行，美国派布林肯执行迄今为止最艰巨的任务——挽救以色列在加沙遭到破坏后的胜利形象。但美国和以色列对此的看法并不一致</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 14:26:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/blinken-comes-to-middle-east-to-clean-up-the-mess-israel-has-made-for-the-u-s/0000018c-e7b7-db55-a39e-f7b7ec0d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列立法者大声疾呼：加沙大规模移民和犹太人定居点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/migration-from-gaza-and-settlement-by-jews-israeli-lawmakers-dont-hide-their-wishes/0000018c-e924-d765-ab9d-f97d6bdb0000</link><description>在一次核心会议上，以色列右翼议员提出了诸如“在加沙地带北部，我们首先必须征服、吞并、摧毁所有房屋”等建议。每次有人提到加沙安置问题，都会爆发出热烈的掌声</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 13:36:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/migration-from-gaza-and-settlement-by-jews-israeli-lawmakers-dont-hide-their-wishes/0000018c-e924-d765-ab9d-f97d6bdb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长向《华尔街日报》表示：真主党知道“我们可以将[加沙]复制粘贴到贝鲁特”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/israeli-defense-minister-to-wsj-hezbollah-knows-we-can-copy-paste-gaza-to-beirut/0000018c-e8c6-d249-a1ce-efc7f72f0000</link><description>国防部长约夫·加兰特对《华尔街日报》表示，“八万人需要能够安全返回家园”，他指的是在黎巴嫩边境附近流离失所的以色列人</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 13:08:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/israeli-defense-minister-to-wsj-hezbollah-knows-we-can-copy-paste-gaza-to-beirut/0000018c-e8c6-d249-a1ce-efc7f72f0000</guid></item><item><title>数十名以色列人阻挡议会呼吁选举，被强行驱散，其中一人被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/dozens-of-israelis-blocking-knesset-to-call-for-elections-forcibly-dispersed-one-arrested/0000018c-e8a8-d765-ab9d-f8fd78200000</link><description>集会上的一名抗议者说，“我的兄弟被谋杀了，因为一个人为了生存而发动了一场针对国家的私人战争”，这次集会是由其成员于 10 月 7 日被杀的家庭组织的。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 11:37:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/dozens-of-israelis-blocking-knesset-to-call-for-elections-forcibly-dispersed-one-arrested/0000018c-e8a8-d765-ab9d-f8fd78200000</guid></item><item><title>在黎巴嫩边境，以色列士兵与看不见的敌人作战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-soldiers-fighting-an-invisible-enemy-on-the-lebanon-border/0000018c-e44c-dc46-a1ec-fefc15d70000</link><description>以色列军队和留在遥远北方的少数居民已经了解了真主党发射反坦克导弹的惯例。但他们无法习惯被搁置的生活</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 11:06:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-soldiers-fighting-an-invisible-enemy-on-the-lebanon-border/0000018c-e44c-dc46-a1ec-fefc15d70000</guid></item><item><title>加沙人可以自由地表达他们对哈马斯和 10 月 7 日袭击事件的看法吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/can-gazans-freely-say-what-they-think-about-hamas-and-the-october-7-attack/0000018c-e4c0-d249-a1ce-efc59aeb0000</link><description>以色列的空袭和炮击造成的死亡和破坏规模削弱了批评或质疑哈马斯战略逻辑的意愿</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 09:58:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/can-gazans-freely-say-what-they-think-about-hamas-and-the-october-7-attack/0000018c-e4c0-d249-a1ce-efc59aeb0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的支持者对他咒骂并撒谎。现在他们需要他来拯救以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/for-months-bibi-ists-cursed-and-lied-about-barak-now-they-need-him-to-save-israel/0000018c-e59e-d249-a1ce-efdff7d40000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的帮派在政府、媒体和街头羞辱了这位前最高法院院长。比比授予巴拉克这个角色，给了他令人印象深刻的认可</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 04:11:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/for-months-bibi-ists-cursed-and-lied-about-barak-now-they-need-him-to-save-israel/0000018c-e59e-d249-a1ce-efdff7d40000</guid></item><item><title>拜登寻求缓和与真主党的关系，极右翼部长使以色列与美国关系紧张</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/far-right-ministers-strain-israel-u-s-ties-as-biden-seeks-deescalation-with-hezbollah/0000018c-e5b8-d765-ab9d-f5fd40f70000</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯自10月7日起开始第四次中东之行，拜登政府担心内塔尼亚胡将与黎巴嫩的冲突升级视为其政治生存的关键</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 04:11:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/far-right-ministers-strain-israel-u-s-ties-as-biden-seeks-deescalation-with-hezbollah/0000018c-e5b8-d765-ab9d-f5fd40f70000</guid></item><item><title>真主党证实高级指挥官死亡；视频显示以色列平民在加沙被扣为人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article-live/hezbollah-confirms-death-of-senior-commander-video-shows-israeli-hostage-in-gaza/0000018c-e702-d765-ab9d-f77fb8fe0000</link><description>真主党精锐部队高级指挥官在以色列发动的袭击中丧生 ■ 两名以色列人在与黎巴嫩边境的不同事件中受伤 ■ 巴勒斯坦伊斯兰圣战组织发布了在加沙扣押人质的视频 ■ 据报道，以色列国防军进入了战争的“新的、较不激烈的阶段” ■ 数十名以色列人抗议者封锁议会入口后强行驱散，高呼“现在就选举” ■ 加沙南部拉法附近的空袭导致三人在车内丧生 ■ 以色列国防军主席称战争将持续一整年</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 03:58:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article-live/hezbollah-confirms-death-of-senior-commander-video-shows-israeli-hostage-in-gaza/0000018c-e702-d765-ab9d-f77fb8fe0000</guid></item></channel></rss>